short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: ReachNotes is a chrome extension for LinkedIn that aggregates ideas for how to best approach individuals.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
ReachNotes enables viewing, adding, and voting on the best inside tips. Add comments to earn more view credits to the app.

The extension will display a nonzero badge on the icon in chrome whenever there are comments detected on an individual. Comments can be added anonymously or with your real name. No comments on a person, add the first one!

Check out www.reachnotes.com for more information.

Questions, feature requests, or bug reports about the app? Please send to reachnotesapp@gmail.com
